body:
I remember my favorite things about console gaming were the massive friends lists, the large parties, and most of all, I could always find someone to game with. Since switching to PC gaming, I've found it's much harder to find large open communities for gamers to socialize, brag about their best games, or just hang out and talk. Well, if anyone is interested, I have an offer.

I am looking for **friendly** League of Legends players, regardless of skill, who want to be more social in game.** If you're 16+, own a mic, and have Discord**, just message _WarTurtle0211_ on discord, or in League Of Legends any time. (Will provide you the link in a chat.)

Hopefully we can keep things civil by enforcing a "Zero Tolerance Policy" in regards to drama. Don't start anything, if you have an issue, approach a server admin, and we will resolve the problem.

We hope to provide a network that will always provide teamates when wanted. But, that is not our only goal. We want members of this server to actively talk about champions, CS techniques, item builds, anything at all league of legends, we urge you to share. As a community we can grow in skill through socialization. **Looking forward to hearing from you!**

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 
_WarTurtle0211_ {{champion:127}} {{champion:202}} {{champion:134}}
